            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-1392] Should not allow to read ACL when not authorized to read node</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-1392</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Not authorized to read, yet still able to list ACL:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;zk: localhost:2181(CONNECTED) 0&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; getAcl /sasltest/n4&lt;br/&gt;
&apos;sasl,&apos;notme@EXAMPLE.COM&lt;br/&gt;
: cdrwa&lt;br/&gt;
